perturbations.original:
\begin{theorem}$($See \cref{section:projective bundle:cor 1}$)$
	For $1\leq k\leq r$, we have morphism $\phi_{k}:Y_{k}\longrightarrow Y_{k-1}$ such that 
	\begin{align*}
		Y_{r}\xrightarrow{\text{$\phi_{r}$}}Y_{r-1}\xrightarrow{\text{$\phi_{r-1}$}}\cdots Y_{2}\xrightarrow{\text{$\phi_{2}$}}Y_{1}\xrightarrow{\text{$\phi_{1}$}}Y_{0}=\{pt\}
	\end{align*}
	is a generalized Bott tower with stage $r$ (see \cref{subsection 2.2} for the Definition of generalized Bott tower).
	\end{theorem}

