\begin{theorem}\label{semistability criterion}
		Let $u\in U_{w}$. Then $uwP/P\in X(w)^{ss}_{T_{J_{r}}}(\mathcal{L}(n\omega_{r}))$ if and only if for every $1\leq j\leq r$, $X_{\beta_{i,j}}(u)\neq 0$ for some $i\in C_{j}$.
